{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 245373, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "让同学们提早适应工作后各种无意义的活动", "timestamp": 1597328494, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 245377, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在中国就是要参加政治生活的……当然这些事也不是强制参加的，不感兴趣不做就是了", "timestamp": 1597328535, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 245380, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "让你不变得孤僻【套用那个帖子里某些人的逻辑】", "timestamp": 1597328542, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 245389, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不光参加无意义，我做过组织者，对于组织者也毫无意义\n实属迷惑", "timestamp": 1597328629, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 245390, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "严格来讲这些应该都是班集体建设、团支部建设、党员组织生活的一部分，但是现在都把经念歪了。", "timestamp": 1597328647, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 245398, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 对组织者有点意义吧，办得好了拿点荣誉，你评奖学金啥的都有用；其他活动（如暑校小导、招生志愿者之类的）也都会看社工简历。当然你要觉得这些都没意义那就确实没意义了。", "timestamp": 1597328720, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 245404, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "说白了还是上面的官僚主义，你一个大学怎么能不建立集体意识呢，怎么量化集体意识？靠搞活动的次数形式呗，管你有没有用，人给我到齐喽。", "timestamp": 1597328765, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 245407, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 好，参与者直接被人当垫脚石", "timestamp": 1597328798, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 246951, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 我也没这么说；事实上组织者办的活动太无聊的话参与者不愿意参加，效果是不好的，对组织者也造不成上述的好处，所以组织者也会尽力迎合参与者的意愿，最后大家都受益。这是理想状态。", "timestamp": 1597372975, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 246955, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不过我也承认事实上是对参与者好处小于对组织者罢了", "timestamp": 1597373020, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2041394, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 46449, "reply_to": 245398, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: ", "timestamp": 1625971706, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 46449, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "我很好奇\n开班会、主题团日、支部事业、党课小组活动意义是什么？", "timestamp": 1597328442, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1625971704, "url": "", "vote": {}}}